{
  "verses": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "text": [
        "Our Help Is in the Name of the LORD"
      ]
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "If the LORD had not been on our side—let Israel now declare—"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "2",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "if the LORD had not been on our sidewhen men attacked us,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "3",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "when their anger flared against us, then they would have swallowed us alive,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "4",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "then the floods would have engulfed us, then the torrent would have overwhelmed us,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "5",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "then the raging waterswould have swept us away."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "6",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Blessed be the LORD, who has not given us as prey to their teeth."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "7",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "We have escaped like a bird from the snare of the fowler; the net is torn, and we have slipped away."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "8",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Our help is in the name of the LORD, the Maker of heaven and earth."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    }
  ]
}